properties.Text:
1)Hit the yellow button.
2)DO NOT STICK AROUND. Green blocks will smash you.
3)Get through the red zone and wait for the red blocks to unlock the teleporter.
4)Enter the teleporter.
5)Repeat.
6)If the green blocks start flashing fast, time's almost up.
This either gets easier or harder. I can't remember.
I definitely remember this last one being super easy.
Here's a tour of the thing. Bye.
You hit the yellow button, but there aren't any yellow blocks. It's probably a metaphor.
These rooms actually are letters. Did you notice?\nI bet you didn't notice.
Don't get used to having time left.\nWe're going to kick it up a notch.
Did you notice how, if you're standing on an unlocked door when the time runs out, you are stuck there forever?\nThat was my idea.
I put this here so you have something to read while you wait.
The problem with lying to you is now there's a breach of trust. Oh, well. Not my problem.
By the way, don't wait around on the teleporters, either.\nYou'll still get flattened.
